OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,FUkraine has launched a "large-scale"
OL,7,Fdrone attack on St Petersburg,
OL,8,Fdemonstrating Kyiv's growing ability
OL,9,Fto hit deep inside Russia.
OL,11,FResidents of the city - the second
OL,12,Flargest in Russia - were told not to
OL,13,Fleave their homes on Saturday
OL,14,Ffollowing the strike, with Governor
OL,15,FAlexander Beglov warning of
OL,16,Fdisruptions to mobile internet
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,19,FThree people sustained minor injuries
OL,20,Fin the attack, Beglov said, and no
OL,21,Fcasualties were reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
