OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FRegional governor Alexander Drozdenko
OL,12,Fsaid 141 drones had been shot down
OL,13,Fover the surrounding Leningrad region
OL,14,Fin an "unprecedented attack", while
OL,15,FRussia's defence ministry said its air
OL,16,Fdefences shot down 376 Ukrainian
OL,17,Fdrones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
