FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,F"It is time to end this war. But
OL,7,FRussia's ruler wants to keep
OL,8,Ffighting," Ukrainian President
OL,9,FVolodymyr Zelenskyy wrote on X,
OL,10,Fsharing footage of the strike's
OL,11,Faftermath.
OL,13,F"Last night, our drones covered a
OL,14,Fdistance of about 1,000 kilometers to
OL,15,Fthe St. Petersburg region ` to the
OL,16,Fenemy navy's arsenals and a base in
OL,17,FKronstad."
OL,19,FZelenskyy said the drones had also hit
OL,20,Fan oil depot in Russia's southern
OL,21,FKrasnodar region.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
