CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,FThe renewed attack on St. Petersburg
OL,7,Fis the latest blow to Russian
OL,8,FPresident Vladimir Putin's efforts to
OL,9,Fcast the conflict as a distant event
OL,10,Fthat doesn't affect Russian daily life.
OL,12,FA Ukrainian drone strike set ablaze an
OL,13,Foil terminal in the city and hit a
OL,14,Fnearby naval base Wednesday, hours
OL,15,Fbefore the opening of the St.
OL,16,FPetersburg International Economic
OL,17,FForum, Putin's annual showcase for
OL,18,Finvestment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,FOn Friday, the Russian president
OL,7,Frejected a proposal by Zelenskyy for a
OL,8,Fface-to-face meeting on the four-year
OL,9,Fconflict, saying he sees "no point" in
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FIn an open letter posted on Thursday,
OL,13,FZelenskyy had acknowledged shifting US
OL,14,Fpriorities, saying it would be wrong
OL,15,Fto simply wait for the Trump
OL,16,Fadministration to turn its focus back
OL,17,Fto ending the war in Ukraine amid the
OL,18,Fconflict in Iran.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,F"When you came to power in Russia more
OL,7,Fthan 26 years ago, many people in
OL,8,FUkraine viewed you positively. That is
OL,9,Fhow it was. But that is now in the
OL,10,Fpast," Zelenskyy wrote to Putin.
OL,12,F"Now, the overwhelming majority of
OL,13,FUkrainians view it positively that our
OL,14,Flong-range drones paid a visit to the
OL,15,Fopening of your forum in St.
OL,16,FPetersburg, covering a distance of
OL,17,Fmore than 1,000 kilometres.
OL,19,F"As you know very well, that distance
OL,20,Fis not the limit of our capabilities."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
