CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,FResponding to Putin's refusal to meet,
OL,7,FUkrainian Foreign Minister Andrii
OL,8,FSybiha said things would "only get
OL,9,Fworse for Russia" in a post on X on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,F"Battlefield losses will continue to
OL,13,Fgrow. Failures will get more
OL,14,Fhumiliating," Sybiha said.
OL,16,F"The economy will plunge deeper into
OL,17,Frecession. More jobs will be lost,
OL,18,Ftaxes will be growing, and inflation
OL,19,Fwill hit those most vulnerable.
OL,26,@pD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780769476
OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,F"There are already no safe places in
OL,7,FRussia that can be exempt from
OL,8,FUkraine's long-range sanctions. But
OL,9,Ftheir intensity will continue to grow."
OL,11,FRussia's defence ministry said on
OL,12,FSaturday it had captured
OL,13,FShevchenko, a settlement in Ukraine's
OL,14,FKharkiv region, according to state
OL,15,Fmedia RIA Novosti.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
