OL,3,CUkraine targets St Petersburg in
OL,4,C'large-scale' drone attack
OL,6,FIn Ukraine, one person was killed and
OL,7,Fthree wounded overnight into Saturday
OL,8,Fin the Dnipropetrovsk region, as
OL,9,FRussian forces struck three districts
OL,10,Fnearly 30 times with drones and
OL,11,Fartillery, regional head Oleksandr
OL,12,FHanzha said.
OL,14,FIn Zaporizhzhia, seven people sought
OL,15,Fmedical care after a Russian drone
OL,16,Fstrike started a fire at a parking
OL,17,Flot, according to regional head Ivan
OL,18,FFedorov.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
